OL,5,FOPENING LEADS continued                
OL,7,GAfterC(a)Gyou should lead a heart.     
OL,8,GWest'sF5SGbid indicates two heart      
OL,9,Glosers, and East's failure to raise to 
OL,10,F6SGshows the same. You will take the   
OL,11,Gfirst two tricks.                      
OL,13,GAfterC(b)Gyou need a good reason not to
OL,14,Glead a heart. It looks like East has   
OL,15,Gfive spades and four diamonds, maybe a 
OL,16,G5-4-2-2 shape withFHAGorFHK,Gso West's 
OL,17,Gheart losers will eventually be thrown 
OL,18,Gon dummy's suits.CMake an attacking    
OL,19,CleadGto establish heart winners.       
