OL,5,FBIDDING QUIZ  REVEAL                   
OL,7,GAt Game All South opens  CSFQ J 10 9 7 
OL,8,F1SGand your partner West CHF9 5 4      
OL,9,Gdoubles for take-out.    CDFA 6 3      
OL,10,GNorth passes. What do youCCFA 5        
OL,11,Gdo with this East hand?                
OL,13,CPRESS REVEAL                           
OL,14,XIf West has a minimum take-out double  
OL,15,Xyou expect at least a 200 penalty. If  
OL,16,XWest has enough for game you'll net at 
OL,17,Xleast 800. In such circumstances if you
OL,18,Xwelcome a trump lead you should pass   
OL,19,Xand take the money!                    
